STATE
v.
Jathlyah al-BAYYINAH. No. 550A03. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2005. Janet Moore, Assistant Public Defender, for Jathiyah al-Bayyinah. Joan Cunningham, Amy C. Kunstling, Assistant Attorney Generals, Garry W. Frank, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th day of April 2005 by Defendant to Stay Decision Pending the U.S. Supreme Court's Decision in Oregon v. Guzek:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference this the 18th day of August 2005."
